Passenger - Class in cscie55.hw3
This class represents a passenger located either inside the elevator or at any floor inside the multi-story building of the Elevator application.
Passenger(int) - Constructor for class cscie55.hw3.Passenger
Creates a Passenger residing on current floor, not queued for boarding any elevator.
passengersDestinedDown - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Floor
List of passengers who are waiting on the floor for DOWN service.
passengersDestinedDownAtThisSecond - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Floor
Number of passengers residing that decide to queue at the elevators for DOWN service at any given second.
passengersDestinedUp - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Floor
List of passengers who are waiting on the floor for UP service.
passengersDestinedUpAtThisSecond - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Floor
Number of passengers residing that decide to queue at the elevators for UP service at any given second.
passengersOnboard - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Elevator
Map that contains the passengers destined for each floor.
passengersResiding - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Floor
Set of passengers residing on this floor, just hanging out.
PassengerStatus - Enum in cscie55.hw3
Enumeration that indicates the status of each passenger in the Elevator application.
PassengerStatus() - Constructor for enum cscie55.hw3.PassengerStatus
 
passengersWaitingForElevatorDown(int) - Method in class cscie55.hw3.Floor

poisson - Variable in class cscie55.hw3.Floor
